decks.notes: The deck focuses on controlling the game through a combination of counterspells, removal spells, and card advantage. Glarb, Calamity's Augur acts as the commander, providing a powerful and versatile control option. The deck includes a range of disruption spells like Thoughtseize, Duress, and Inquisition of Kozilek to strip opponents of their key cards. It also features versatile counterspells such as Counterspell, Cryptic Command, and Force of Will to stop threats in their tracks. Card advantage is provided through cards like Brainstorm, Snapcaster Mage, and Mystic Sanctuary. The deck aims to outvalue and outmaneuver opponents through careful resource management and timing of spells to eventually secure a win.
